{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488790/extras/image.png?t=1739333134\" />The newly renovated haunted house, <i>Hiyoshi Clinic</i>, was quickly becoming the centerpiece of Horizon Amusement Park. The protagonist, journalist Eiji Sakuma, visits the attraction for a report and finds himself immersed in a series of terrifying performances that seem far too real. Guided by a child's voice, he begins to experience strange phenomena.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore a haunted mansion set in a 1940s setting in FPS mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488790/extras/image4.png?t=1739333134\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The eerie interior has been renovated while still retaining some of its original appearance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488790/extras/image2.png?t=1739333134\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Inside the haunted mansion, there are puzzles and attractions to enjoy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488790/extras/image3.png?t=1739333134\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There is also a collection element where you can collect the dolls placed inside the mansion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Early Access version is designed to offer approximately 60 minutes of gameplay, depending on how you play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Allows game commentary and broadcasting.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488790/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739333134","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com